8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both n8n and Pipefy share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where n8n pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Support, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, n8n holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Pipefy scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both n8n and Pipefy offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. n8n's free tier and Pipefy's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
